devdoc.details: This contract is designed to be called via delegatecall from a main loan contract,      so it does not maintain its own storage context for loans or parameters.

CollateralRatioPercent(uint16).details: Reverts if p == 0 or above 30.00% (3000 bps).

params.p: New collateral ratio in basis points.

ManagementWallet(address).details: Reverts if w is the zero address or this contract's own address.

MaxNPLPercent(uint16).details: Reverts if p is above 50.00% (5000 bps).

params.p: New maximum NPL ratio in basis points.

MonthlyInterestPercent(uint16).details: Reverts if the interest is zero or above 20.00% (2000 bps).

params.p: New interest rate in basis points (e.g., 1000 = 10.00%).

PenaltyPercent(uint16).details: Reverts if the penalty is zero or above 50.00% (5000 bps).

params.p: New penalty percentage in basis points.

TP().details: Reverts if no profit is available or transfer fails.
